reviews.review_text:
Awesome sound! You can always trust Sennheisers to put you right in the middle of the crowd at a Dead show.  If they're good enough for Healy, they're good enough for anyone. :-)

This has definitely made my "must have AUDs" list.
4-30-84 Excellent aud recording. Real nice show too!

Beware This show is evil. The music is good above par maybe, but listen closely to the space, and you may come to a similar conclusion. April 30th is a day full of History. Only thing missing from this 4/30 is the Peggy-O. Anyways, don't let it scare you, Jerry always wins in the end, But the evil almost overwhelms them in this one. Listen for yourself. Its not called Nastaar Coiliseum for nothing. Just ask Justin. 5 stars for absolute insanity and the evil that manifests itself, the recording is good, way better than the tape my friend Chris made at this show with his old Marantz thing. We have listened to this show about 1200 times, so far. Try other 4/30's, they are all very very interesting. Thanks Charlie.
Par On point and standard, No Highlights
